{"tid":840291,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[風化朗] 德媒曝C.朗拿度涉嫌性侵 事後付對方封口費達和解","createTime":"2018-09-28T15:14:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-29T03:14:11.000Z","uid":34571,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dc620b3866b1a2649f5ba980429cd2faf29a1521","tid":840291,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:14:52.000Z","msg":"據德國《明鏡週刊》爆料，一位來自拉斯維加斯的女士指控稱，C.朗拿度在2009年於一家酒店中強姦了自己。當時雙方於庭外達成和解，但現在該女士要求重審此案。<br />\n<br />\n　　2017年時，《明鏡週刊》就報導過這一消息，並表示C.朗拿度為此事向該女性支付了封口費。C.朗拿度經理人文迪斯創辦的經紀公司則表示這篇報導純屬虛構，並稱這一指控噁心而過分。"},{"pid":"58aebb107c40b3d811c9ea36e96037dcecdbf15f","tid":840291,"uid":90515,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:20:59.000Z","msg":"告鳩埋美斯就啱，凌辱左阿朗同拉莫斯咁耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fdf37f88a7a65e1a4326ea20f9f0578ba13fbeb6","tid":840291,"uid":96877,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:22:22.000Z","msg":"睇錯我朗強姦自己"},{"pid":"fdfc335a659f2f7d96a9bcf615225759fa46a7e2","tid":840291,"uid":1790,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:22:45.000Z","msg":"賤朗有咩做唔出"},{"pid":"d1a5bc0bbf2cef25d91233dc4d098adfcc185db4","tid":840291,"uid":106426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T15:23:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"59aca38f1d65bbd8f27a8636216b2d063bf9b233","tid":840291,"uid":57237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T16:24:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img